title: Disney Movie - The Legend of Lobo (1962)
description:
One of the many nature movies produced by Disney in the 60&#039;s, it&#039;s really hard to find and the DVD is very expensive. Enjoy

The Legend of Lobo (1962) is a film about a family of wolves. There is no dialogue but, but it is narrated by Rex Allen. In contrast to other movies about wolves, this movie is very different. They are neither sugarcoated nor vilified, but rather are shown to be both an efficient predator and a devoted parent in times of encroaching human settlement.
